Steps to install Sass:

1. Cloned the repository:
   git clone https://github.com/trizahc/alx-intermediate-frontend.git

2. Navigated into the directory:
   cd alx-intermediate-frontend

3. Created a new directory for Sass files:
   mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   cd 0x03-sass_scss

4. Installed Sass using npm (latest version):
   npm install sass

5. Verified the installation by running:
   npx sass --version
